  <entry>
    <title>用gitee/github+picgo制作博客图床</title>
    <link href="https://linblog.ga/2020/12/19/%E7%94%A8gitee-github-picgo%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/"/>
    <id>https://linblog.ga/2020/12/19/%E7%94%A8gitee-github-picgo%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/</id>
    <published>2020-12-19T15:16:49.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-06-18T23:43:48.860Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>大家好可以看见我之前的文章基本没有什么图片</p><p>原因是我没有图床啊</p><blockquote><p>有人问了:<code>github</code>不是有空间放吗？</p></blockquote><p>你们想啊！</p><p>github那速度<code>简直</code><strong><em>*</em></strong></p><p>我也想过<code>gitee</code>可是如果我写文章难道要打开终端新建md</p><p>然后打开github/gitee上传图片<br>再在vscode粘贴<code>![****](****)</code><br>写博客吗</p><p>我查阅了大量资料教大家搭建自己的博客图床</p><h1 id="正文"><a href="#正文" class="headerlink" title="正文"></a>正文</h1><h2 id="需要："><a href="#需要：" class="headerlink" title="需要："></a>需要：</h2><p>gitee/github的账号</p><p>安装<a href="https://github.com/Molunerfinn/PicGo/releases">picgo</a>(mac选dmg，windows选exe)</p><h2 id="个人访问令牌"><a href="#个人访问令牌" class="headerlink" title="个人访问令牌"></a>个人访问令牌</h2><p>在<a href="https://github.com/settings/tokens">这里</a>生成新令牌tokens，<br>note随便填，勾选<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/qilinge1273/qilinge-img//20201219154855.png" alt=""><br>点击绿色按钮把绿勾旁边一大串复制下来，退出这个界面可就没了！</p><h2 id="配置picgo"><a href="#配置picgo" class="headerlink" title="配置picgo"></a>配置picgo</h2><h3 id="GitHub"><a href="#GitHub" class="headerlink" title="GitHub"></a>GitHub</h3><p>右键这个<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/qilinge1273/qilinge-img//20201219155302.png" alt="">打开详细窗口<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/qilinge1273/qilinge-img//20201219155449.png" alt=""></p><p>打开图床设置的GitHub图床</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/qilinge1273/qilinge-img//20201219155658.png" alt="">的格式是<code>GitHub用户名/仓库</code></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/qilinge1273/qilinge-img//20201219155821.png" alt="">填main或master</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/qilinge1273/qilinge-img//20201219160715.png" alt="">填刚刚生成的tokens</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/qilinge1273/qilinge-img//20201219161014.png" alt="">填写图片存放的文件夹</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/qilinge1273/qilinge-img//20201219161823.png" alt="">由于国内访问raw会很慢或不能访问所以用cdn</p><p>点击确定和设为默认图床接下来就可以把图片拖进框框里上传啦！</p><h3 id="gitee码云"><a href="#gitee码云" class="headerlink" title="gitee码云"></a>gitee码云</h3><p>右键这个<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/qilinge1273/qilinge-img//20201219155302.png" alt="">打开详细窗口<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/qilinge1273/qilinge-img//20201219155449.png" alt=""></p><p>打开<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/qilinge1273/qilinge-img//20201219162712.png" alt="">搜索gitee<br>安装插件重启应用图床设置就多了一个gitee</p><p>打开gitee</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/qilinge1273/qilinge-img//20201219162959.png" alt="">的格式是<code>Gitee用户名/仓库</code></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/qilinge1273/qilinge-img//20201219163124.png" alt="">填写分支，默认是master</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/qilinge1273/qilinge-img//20201219163346.png" alt="">填写gitee的tokens（生成方法和GitHub差不多）</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/qilinge1273/qilinge-img//20201219163628.png" alt="">由于gitee是国内的所以可以不用填</p><p>点击确定和设为默认图床接下来就可以把图片拖进框框里上传啦</p><p>当然还可以设置其他图床可以设置自行去看其他博主的视频</p><p>这里推荐几个插件大家可以去搜<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/qilinge1273/qilinge-img//20201219164234.png" alt=""></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;大家好可以看见我之前的文章基本没有什么图片&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;原因是我没有图床啊&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;有人问了:&lt;code&gt;github&lt;/code&gt;不是有空间放吗？&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;你们想啊！&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;github那速度&lt;c</summary>
      
    
    
    
    
